snippet.title: The Bugs Bunny Crazy Castle 2:  Part 1 of 18
snippet.description:
This video is of stages 1 through 4.  It is not a speed run, though played fairly perfectly.  I apologize for the sound going out of sync as the video continues.

Stage 1 & 2:  Almost perfect speed runs.  Stage 2 in particular would be very, very difficult to accomplish faster.

Stage 3:  Finesse with the lightning bolt.  All enemies killed.

Stage 4:  Took a little time to collect and use the bombs on two coyote.
